RIFT VALLEY FEVER IN ZIMBABWE
(Date of last previously reported outbreak: June 1999).
Extract from the monthly report of Zimbabwe for June 2001, received
from Dr Stuart K. Hargreaves, Director of Veterinary Services,
Ministry of Agriculture, Harare:
